Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.56,0:02:03.33,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,"Piccolo Daimao and\Nthe Super Giant Technique"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.85,0:02:18.44,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡Son-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.14,0:02:46.98,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡¿Qué demonios?! ¡Lo resistió!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.69,0:03:00.52,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡Maldita sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.52,0:03:04.26,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,Aunque solo fue por\nun instante...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.50,0:03:09.59,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡...me asustaste de muerte!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.90,0:03:16.53,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,Impresionante. Y esa Mega\N{\i1}Kamehameha{\i0} también era mi carta de triunfo...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.35,0:03:29.45,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡Me las vas a {\i1}pagar{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.45,0:03:33.39,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡Voy a hacerte pedazos!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.67,0:03:52.07,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,T-Tengo miedo...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.08,0:03:58.58,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,S-Son Gokú let off a tremendous,\Nmind-boggling attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.58,0:04:06.32,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡P-Pero aún más increíble es\nque\nMa-Junior lo haya resistido!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.32,0:04:10.26,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡Y solo se le ha roto la ropa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.26,0:04:13.42,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¿Oh? ¿Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.17,0:04:22.10,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¿No lo he visto en algún lugar antes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.11,0:04:23.83,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¿Pero dónde?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.88,0:04:32.37,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,Creo recordar haberlo visto antes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.68,0:04:36.85,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡Oye! ¿¡No es él?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.85,0:04:40.69,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡Nada bueno! ¡Ahora su verdadera\nidentidad está al descubierto!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.69,0:04:43.36,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡Esto se va a convertir en una mala situación!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.36,0:04:45.46,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡Se parece a él!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.46,0:04:47.95,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,Like Piccolo Daimao!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.50,0:04:51.33,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,Piccolo Daimao?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.34,0:04:53.33,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡Ahora que lo mencionas!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.37,0:04:58.51,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡No puede ser!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.51,0:05:02.84,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,Is it really... Piccolo Daimao?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.82,0:05:09.25,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡Sí! ¡Se parece a él!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.25,0:05:10.69,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡{\i1}Exactamente{\i0} como él!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.69,0:05:14.36,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡¿No es obvio?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.36,0:05:17.89,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,I am Piccolo Daimao, reborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.84,0:05:29.07,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡Oh, mierda!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.07,0:05:31.84,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡Difundan la noticia por el mundo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.84,0:05:37.71,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,After I've put an end to Son Gokú,\NI will become your king once again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.71,0:05:42.38,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,Piccolo-{\i1}sama{\i0} will once again\Nreign as the world's strongest!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.28,0:07:09.32,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡Las cosas se han complicado\nde\nrepente!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:14.73,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,Ma-Junior was in fact Piccolo Daimao!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.03,0:07:20.77,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡Qué profesional...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.77,0:07:24.13,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,Está tranquilo ahora que la basura se ha ido.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.94,0:07:30.84,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡Ustedes también, retírense!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.84,0:07:33.38,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡Será más fácil para mí pelear así!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.38,0:07:34.68,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡Bien!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:37.18,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡Vamos cerca de Ten Shin Han y los\ndemás!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.18,0:07:42.21,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,Eh... um... esperen un segundo...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.09,0:07:46.85,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,Ugh... Oh, está bien...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.63,0:07:51.16,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡No te nos mueras, Gokú!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.16,0:07:54.16,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,No se preocupen, ¡no dejaré que eso pase!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.84,0:07:59.60,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,Les digo desde ya, ¡no hay\nmanera de\nque los deje ganar el título!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.61,0:08:04.88,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡Guarda esa confianza para\n{\i1}después{\i0}\nde que veas mi siguiente técnica!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.88,0:08:06.37,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡¿Qué?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.88,0:08:45.25,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¿Q-Qué está pasando?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.05,0:09:21.55,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,- ¿¡Qué es {\i1}eso{\i0}?!\N- ¡Esto no puede ser!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.55,0:09:23.65,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡Esto es una locura!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.56,0:09:31.96,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡N-No puede ser!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.73,0:10:10.74,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,Parece que tu fin está cerca por fin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.74,0:10:14.60,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡Vaya! ¡Menudo tamaño!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.91,0:10:23.38,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡¿No va contra las reglas?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.38,0:10:27.92,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,N-No, no hay reglas en\ncontra de\ncrecer...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.92,0:10:31.15,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡¿A quién le importa el combate ahora?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.17,0:10:43.19,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡Muere!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.64,0:10:54.55,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,{\i1}¡{\i0}Nosotros somos los que estamos en peligro!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.88,0:11:26.07,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡E-Es rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:33.68,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡Oh, oh! ¡Nada bueno!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.93,0:11:41.23,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,Gokú!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.23,0:11:44.03,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡Gokú-{\i1}san{\i0}! ¡Levántate!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.14,0:11:50.56,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,- Gokú!\N- Son-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.56,0:11:52.12,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡Levántate!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.09,0:12:10.61,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡Gokú! ¡Te ayudaremos!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.36,0:12:13.02,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡N-No, deténganse!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.03,0:12:14.52,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡¿Qué?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.77,0:12:24.00,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡Si me ayudan, perderé mi\noportunidad\nde obtener el título!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.52,0:12:28.85,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¿Estás {\i1}seguro{\i0} de que no\nquieres que\ntus amigos te ayuden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.85,0:12:31.32,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡No hay manera de que puedas ganar!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.32,0:12:33.99,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡E-Es todo un enemigo temible!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.99,0:12:38.23,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡A pesar de haber crecido en tamaño,\nsu\nvelocidad no ha cambiado en absoluto!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.23,0:12:42.67,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡Incluso con tu tamaño actual,\nno eres\nnada de qué preocuparse!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.67,0:12:44.70,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¿Nada de qué preocuparse, dices?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.70,0:12:46.53,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡Así es!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.63,0:13:15.46,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,Esto no puede ser...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.14,0:13:27.21,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡I-Increíble!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.21,0:13:29.77,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡Es gigantesco, pero Gokú lo lanzó\Ncomo si no pesara nada!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.16,0:13:42.93,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¿¡Qué tipo de entrenamiento hizo Gokú?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.93,0:13:45.96,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¿Te diste cuenta, Krilin?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.96,0:13:52.90,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡No se ha vuelto más débil, a pesar de haber\Nlanzado una {\i1}Kamehameha{\i0} tan intensa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.90,0:13:56.31,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡Ahora que lo mencionas, tienes razón!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.31,0:13:58.07,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡Sigue así!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.91,0:14:04.65,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,Astuto bastardo...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.32,0:14:09.76,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,No me importa que seas {\i1}tan\ngrande{\i0}...\n¡No me das miedo en absoluto!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.76,0:14:13.72,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,Aunque estaría en problemas\nsi fueras\naún más grande...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.03,0:14:21.23,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¿Crees que no puedo crecer más que esto?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.24,0:14:22.40,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡¿Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.40,0:14:26.36,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡N-No lo dices en serio!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.29,0:15:01.63,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡E-Esto no puede estar pasando!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.63,0:15:03.79,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡Esto no es real, ¿verdad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.88,0:15:19.51,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡Vaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.51,0:15:21.48,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¿Qué opinas de esto?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.48,0:15:23.71,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡E-Esto es una locura!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.72,0:15:33.22,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡I-Increíblemente grande! ¡Su tamaño ha\naumentado aún más que antes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.30,0:15:39.27,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,Run, Gokú!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.27,0:15:42.17,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡Ríndete!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:45.84,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡Dudo que puedas levantar mi dedo {\i1}ahora{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.84,0:15:48.21,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡¿Entonces qué vas a hacer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.21,0:15:51.77,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡Caíste! ¡He estado esperando\neste\nmomento!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.05,0:15:55.45,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡Mal perdedor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.86,0:16:07.85,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,Gokú disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.90,0:16:13.43,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡¿Q-Qué demonios?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.43,0:16:15.94,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡Gokú entró en su boca!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.94,0:16:17.63,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡¿Dentro de su boca?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.87,0:16:49.10,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡Son!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.10,0:16:51.40,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡Ten Shin Han! ¡Atrapa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.81,0:17:00.85,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡E-Esto es!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.85,0:17:03.12,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡Ábrelo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.12,0:17:04.58,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡Bien!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:08.96,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡¿La botella en la que Dios fue sellado?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.96,0:17:10.92,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡¿Qué?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.19,0:17:14.53,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.37,0:17:25.96,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡Muy bien!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.82,0:17:42.42,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¿Q-Qué? ¿Cómo estuve?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.42,0:17:44.05,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡Maldita sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.53,0:17:49.46,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡¿Q-Qué acaba de pasar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.07,0:17:55.93,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!\NNow there's {\i1}two{\i0} Piccolo Daimaos!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.64,0:17:59.73,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,Eres Dios, ¿verdad?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.14,0:18:09.75,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,Gokú empleó una estrategia de\Ncombate brillante para rescatarte.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.75,0:18:11.68,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Gokú{\i0} did?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.32,0:18:18.09,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,Ahora recuerdo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.09,0:18:22.06,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,Recibí el {\i1}Mafuba{\i0} de vuelta,\ny luego...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.06,0:18:25.50,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡¿Por qué tú?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.18,0:18:39.21,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¿Oh? ¿Volviendo a la normalidad?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.21,0:18:42.18,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡C-Cállate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.18,0:18:47.85,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,A menos que quieras que te\ngolpeen\ndesde dentro otra vez.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.76,0:19:22.49,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡No puedo verlos!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.49,0:19:25.25,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡Ni siquiera yo, Dios, puedo verlos!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.83,0:19:33.36,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡En el aire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.14,0:20:16.58,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,Gokú!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.75,0:20:26.58,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kamehame...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.82,0:20:32.49,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...ha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.20,0:20:42.37,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡¿Q-Qué demonios?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.37,0:20:44.44,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡S-Sus pies!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.44,0:20:46.10,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡Hizo la {\i1}Kamehameha{\i0} con los pies!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.88,0:20:53.15,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡Brillante! ¡Al usar los pies para hacer la\N{\i1}Kamehameha{\i0}, ha liberado sus manos!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.15,0:20:56.67,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡Qué chico tan ingenioso!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.79,0:21:39.02,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,N-Nada bueno... bajé la guardia...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.76,0:21:42.35,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡Ahí viene!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.14,0:21:49.90,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¡Muere!
